item.title: End of Internship
item.description: Yesterday was the last day of my internship at Terato Tech, 20 weeks has passed by so quickly. I had a lot of fun, learned a lot of new stuffs, and last but not least, met a lot of interesting people. I had to leave the project I was working on, and that is a little bit sad, but I hope I can at least tie up some of the loose ends before I stop working on it to move on the next project.
